в”‚ Features: в”‚
в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ MFA (TOTP) в”‚
в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Social login (Azure AD, Google) в”‚
в”‚ в””в”Ђв”Ђ JWT Access Tokens (RS256) в”‚

1. Angular в†’ Keycloak (Authorization Request + PKCE)
2. User logs in в†’ MFA challenge
3. Keycloak в†’ Angular (Authorization Code)
4. Angular в†’ Keycloak (Code + Verifier в†’ Access Token + Refresh Token)
5. Angular в†’ .NET API (Bearer JWT in Authorization header)
6. .NET API в†’ validates JWT signature against Keycloak JWKS endpoint
7. .NET API в†’ checks role claims в†’ authorize/deny
